</a>. This tau average grows smoothly with <i>a</i><sup id=3D"cite_ref-104"=
 class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Euclidean_alg=
orithm#cite_note-104"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>103<span class=
=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup><sup id=3D"cite_ref-105" class=3D"refer=
