nt <i>C</i> in this formula is called <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w=
iki/Porter%27s_constant" title=3D"Porter's constant">Porter's constant</a><=
sup id=3D"cite_ref-106" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia=
.org/wiki/Euclidean_algorithm#cite_note-106"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[=
