        <mo>.</mo>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle \omega =3D{\s=
qrt {D}}.}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/0a727dc9de031c71ccacf6617ac07a816ed3ba3b" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.671ex; width:9.051ex; height:3.009ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle \om=
ega =3D{\sqrt {D}}.}"></span></dd></dl>
<p>If, however, <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>D</i></span> does equal a multip=
le of four plus one, then
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
s=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyl=
e \omega =3D{\frac {1+{\sqrt {D}}}{2}}.}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <mi>=CF=89<!-- =CF=89 --></mi>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mfrac>
            <mrow>
              <mn>1</mn>
              <mo>+</mo>
              <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                <msqrt>
                  <mi>D</mi>
                </msqrt>
              </mrow>
            </mrow>
            <mn>2</mn>
          </mfrac>
        </mrow>
        <mo>.</mo>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
